FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772831513
OL,3,C'Infected water crisis changed our
OL,4,Clives forever'
OL,6,FThe company today (March 4) pleaded
OL,7,Fguilty to supplying water that was
OL,8,Funfit for human consumption' following
OL,9,Fthe crisis in 2024, which affected
OL,10,Fthousands of households in the south
OL,11,FDevon town.
OL,13,FThe parasite was discovered in the
OL,14,Fwater supply in May 2024, leading to a
OL,15,F'boil water' notice issued to around
OL,16,F16,000 homes and hundreds of people
OL,17,Freporting sickness and diarrhoea.
OL,19,F'You feel helpless'
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772831513
OL,3,C'Infected water crisis changed our
OL,4,Clives forever'
OL,6,FAron Davis' son Michael, who was aged
OL,7,Fthree when the crisis began, is Type 1
OL,8,Fdiabetic.
OL,10,FWhen the bacteria was discovered and
OL,11,Fresidents were told not to drink from
OL,12,Ftheir taps, Aron recalls going on a
OL,13,Fdesperate hunt for safe water.
OL,15,F"I had to scour the whole of Torbay,"
OL,16,Fhe said. "I got lucky getting just one
OL,17,Fbottle of water.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772831513
OL,3,C'Infected water crisis changed our
OL,4,Clives forever'
OL,6,F"I was ringing up South West Water,
OL,7,Fasking them for water. We had to go on
OL,8,Fa priority register, (which) we
OL,9,Fweren't even told about.
OL,11,F"We didn't really get any notice. A
OL,12,Fletter posted through the door saying
OL,13,F'Boil water notice', and that was it.
OL,15,F"You feel helpless, don't you? All
OL,16,Fyou're trying to do is right by your
OL,17,Fkids. If his blood sugar glucose
OL,18,Flevels go too high, he needs water."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772831513
OL,3,C'Infected water crisis changed our
OL,4,Clives forever'
OL,6,FAron's partner became unwell, and as
OL,7,Fthe number of Cryptosporidiosis cases
OL,8,Fcontinued to rise, the family gave up
OL,9,Fdrinking from the tap. Aron says they
OL,10,Fmay never do so again.
OL,12,F"It's too dangerous," he said. "I
OL,13,Fwon't risk him getting poorly again.
OL,14,FEven if they told me it's safe, I
OL,15,Fstill won't give it to him. Not worth
OL,16,Fthe risk."
OL,18,F'It has devastated our lives'
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772831513
OL,3,C'Infected water crisis changed our
OL,4,Clives forever'
OL,6,FJen Watts says her ten-year-old son,
OL,7,FRaffi, became seriously unwell and
OL,8,Flater developed an eating disorder
OL,9,Fknown as Arfid (Avoidant/Restrictive
OL,10,FFood Intake Disorder).
OL,12,F"He's now eating a very restricted
OL,13,Fdiet of food, which is a good step in
OL,14,Fthe right direction for him, but he is
OL,15,Fa long way short of having a normal
OL,16,Fdiet," Jen said.
OL,18,F"It really has devastated our lives
OL,19,Fever since. It's not been the same at
OL,20,Fall."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772831513
OL,3,C'Infected water crisis changed our
OL,4,Clives forever'
OL,6,FJen says many people feel strongly
OL,7,Fthat South West Water should accept
OL,8,Fresponsibility for what went wrong.
OL,10,F"The handling of the whole situation
OL,11,Fwas nothing short of abysmal," she
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,F"They need to be held accountable for
OL,15,Fit because it shouldn't have happened
OL,16,Fin the first place.
OL,18,F"Children like my son have been so
OL,19,Ftremendously affected.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772831513
OL,3,C'Infected water crisis changed our
OL,4,Clives forever'
OL,6,F"There may well be lots of periods in
OL,7,Fhis life where he significantly
OL,8,Fstruggles with food and drink, and
OL,9,Fthat should never have happened. He
OL,10,Fshould never have got this infection
OL,11,Fin the first place."
OL,13,FThere were, in total, 143 confirmed
OL,14,Fcases of Cryptosporidiosis in Brixham
OL,15,Fin 2024, with four hospitalisations.
OL,17,FThe Drinking Water Inspectorate
OL,18,Flaunched a prosecution of South West
OL,19,FWater Limited for potential offences
OL,20,Funder section 70(1) of the Water
OL,21,FIndustry Act 1991.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772831513
OL,3,C'Infected water crisis changed our
OL,4,Clives forever'
OL,6,FThe hearing is due to take place on
OL,7,FWednesday, March 4th at Exeter
OL,8,FMagistrates' Court.
OL,10,FA spokesman for South West Water said:
OL,11,F"We are sorry for the impact the
OL,12,Fincident in the Brixham area in 2024
OL,13,Fhad on the local community and
OL,14,Fvisitors, and we take any reports of
OL,15,Fillness extremely seriously. However,
OL,16,Fwe are unable to comment on individual
OL,17,Fcases."
OL,26,@sD@AOUyD@GO]
